book-vector — attribution for source data

CMU Book Summary Dataset
------------------------
Plot summaries and metadata are derived from the CMU Book Summary Dataset
(David Bamman, Carnegie Mellon University), which is released under a
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike License (CC BY-SA).

    https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~dbamman/booksummaries.html

The plot summaries themselves originate from Wikipedia and are likewise
CC BY-SA. Any redistributed data derived from these summaries (e.g. extracted
facet fields, embeddings) is provided under the same CC BY-SA terms, with
attribution as above.

TVTropes / DBTropes (optional, non-critical enrichment)
-------------------------------------------------------
If TVTropes-derived trope data is used, note it is licensed CC BY-NC-SA 3.0
(NonCommercial). It is kept off the critical path (see PLAN.md, D2) and must
